Hi welcome to sharing at TPB. I see our dear friend SnakEye and the mod have already advised you about duplicate torrents. If you want to have a torrent deleted, this is the thread to post in:
https://forum.suprbay.org/showthread.php?tid=125073
It is a good idea to register on the Suprbay forum anyway and set up your own thread, that way you can take and respond to requests, get information, etc. Also always a good idea to run a search before uploading to make sure SnakEye or someone else didn't share it first, don't want to step on anyone's toesies.
